data.text:
Mura is a municipality in the province of Barcelona and autonomous community of Catalonia, Spain. The municipality covers an area of 47.78 square kilometres (18.45 sq mi) and the population in 2014 was 211.

Map of 08278 Mura, Barcelona, Spain
